{"tid":1717483,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【係時候為這場流血的革命命名】","createTime":"2019-11-13T15:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T11:54:55.000Z","uid":272825,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1e5b5f646cae13b825b21e0dae5074c0ae9530d7","tid":1717483,"uid":272825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:23:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果繼續叫「反送中」，我覺得已經唔合適，<br />\n因為「反送中」一早已經成功。<br />\n<br />\n所以「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">名正則言順，言順則事成</span></span>」，<br />\n有返個好聽既革命名，<br />\n一定會更加<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">出師有名</span></span>，<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建議做法：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. <span style=\"color: pink;\">集思廣益</span>，諗一個大部分手足都認同既革命稱號<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣</span>幫手製作海報、傳開、翻譯成各國語言<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聯絡外國記者，傳到全世界都知</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求！缺一不可！<br />\n解散黑警！刻不容緩！</span></span>"},{"pid":"aeed40e1d459947a97495e9e20e068ef205be339","tid":1717483,"uid":272825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:24:23.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"3f6370333d1c6ce3447a47357e305f2291425a67","tid":1717483,"uid":272825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:24:34.000Z","msg":"自推十次　９"},{"pid":"35fe0bae9aedf79feb2657ecdbe601e0c33e42e1","tid":1717483,"uid":272825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:24:46.000Z","msg":"自推十次　８"},{"pid":"2ed5857af72a11369b11a68aac637ec6e48beed6","tid":1717483,"uid":272825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:24:58.000Z","msg":"自推十次　７"},{"pid":"4f5ae3ec2308dd347debd6e3c4e112db8663bca6","tid":1717483,"uid":272825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:25:25.